                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <placeName>Louisville Ky</placeName>\n                                        <date>January 15th 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                                        <placeName>Ph<hi rend=\"sup\">a</hi></placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Respected and Dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p>I hope that you are home by this time and that your trip\n                                                  <sic>trough</sic> the states<lb/> will have had\n                                        the effect of improving your health and of\n                                                  <sic>strenghtening</sic> and<lb/> renewing your\n                                        energies to future spiritual labor.</p>\n                              <p>I am in possession of your kind letter dated <placeName>St.\n                                                  Louis</placeName>\n                                        <date>Dec. 18th</date> but fearing the<lb/> answer would not\n                                        reach you in time, as there <sic>were</sic> no mail-boats\n                                                  <del>g</del> running,<lb/> I thought it advisable\n                                        to omit it.</p>\n                              <p>With this letter I mail one to the Asmonean containing a statement\n                                        of<lb/> the proceedings taken in your behalf, while in this\n                                        city. I will give you<lb/> on the other side the substance\n                                        of my correspondence, which would have<lb/> reached\n                                                  <placeName>New York</placeName> long before this,\n                                        were it not for an approval it had<lb/> to undergo at our\n                                        Board of Trustees.</p>\n                              <p>I am inclined to believe that all your subscribers would like to\n                                        receive<lb/> the Occident for <date>January</date>, as they,\n                                        or the most of them, are <del>desirou</del><lb/> desirous to\n                                        know something of your doings in other places also. I<lb/>\n                                        would therefore humbly advise you to begin with the next\n                                        number,<lb/> if you deem it expedient and till<add>?</add>\n                                        up to spirit charge your abane<add>?</add>.</p>\n                              <p>Please let me hear from you, as soon you are arrived in\n                                                  <placeName>Ph<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                                        >a</hi></placeName><lb/> my wife requested me to give you\n                                        her best respects.<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Straus</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Lirhten<add>?</add></persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Lowensohn</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Oberudarfer</persName> and all your\n                                        friends—and<lb/> there are a good many—return their\n                                        heartfelt regard and esteem<lb/> to you.</p>\n                              <p>May the Lord grant you many years of uninterrupted health and\n                                        happi<lb/>ness, to enable you to reap the fruits of your\n                                        sowing.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Your devoted friend and obedient servant</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">BHGotthelf</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3v698z3j/canvas/p1"
                }
